originalText.text: I've been living in Manhattan for over a decade and there was no way I could've found my dream apartment without Dan's help. I was being spammed by all the listing sites you can imagine before I found Defiant Realty and started working with Dan. After 2 brief conversations, Dan helped narrow my search and got me a deal on an apartment I thought was out of my price range. Dan was upfront with me about each building we saw, the brokerage fee etc and it was him who recommended a no fee apartment I thought was completely out of my range. I've recommended him to my friends and co-workers and would use him again in a heartbeat, but under his guidance I signed a multiyear lease :)
